Jennifer_Blood_-_First_Blood_Vol_1_TPB_(2013)_(Digital)_(DR_&_Quinch-Empire)


Jessie Blute's uncles murdered her father and drove her mother to suicide, which forced Jessie to fake her own death. With a new identity, she distanced herself from her past, found love, raised a family... And then, many years later, she sought out her uncles and delivered brutal and blood-drenched vengeance.

Collected in Jennifer Blood: First Blood.
